{"tid":302993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[留名等笑] 鐘樓集會","createTime":"2017-06-29T22:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T06:18:47.000Z","uid":17510,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab79859cb70cce358667ddbd5522d313bc231bdf","tid":302993,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T22:08:55.000Z","msg":"連登仔講就天下無敵<br />\n<br />\n咩帶定口罩等住比警犬清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪唔好再講要返工不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心講句  到時有一百人出席都偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得<br />\n港豬係豬黎架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天生就係要比人劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雜種就係今次既屠夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警犬咁撚夠彊出反對通知書<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n而家唔係我地而係警犬煽動我地暴動<br />\n<br />\n還我集會自由<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立  你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"58f285c18a44158342631d19cfcfdbcbb5f5b71c","tid":302993,"uid":17510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T22:12:08.000Z","msg":"支那人就係鐘意胡亂行使象徵式權力<br />\n<br />\n今次唔還以顏色   我地將永無立足之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a3b18aff31efa2443690fe5bdf9736ff4ff29b","tid":302993,"uid":120070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T22